Handles:
- Initial measurement via ResizeObserver
- Dynamic resizing when container size changes
- Fallback to default SLOT_ROW_HEIGHT if container not ready

Usage:
```tsx
const { rowHeight, containerHeight, isReady } = useTimelineHeight(
  gridWrapperRef,
  dateRowsLength
);
// Use rowHeight in grid cell height calculations
```

